      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">13.002</ph> Purpose.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The purpose of this part is to prescribe simplified acquisition procedures in order to-</p>
         <ol id="d723e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d750e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Reduce administrative costs;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d750e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            Improve opportunities for small, small disadvantaged, women-owned, veteran-owned, HUBZone, and service-disabled veteran-owned small business concerns to obtain a fair proportion of Government contracts;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d750e22">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            Promote efficiency and economy in contracting; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d750e27">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
						            Avoid unnecessary burdens for agencies and contractors.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
